title: Dreams and dreaming (Time-Life Mysteries of the Unknown)
description:
pdf / English / 1990 Time-Life / 160 pages / ISBN 10 080946389X / 25.8 mb

Dreams are some of the most enigmatic and whimsical aspects of the human psyche. Thus, there are various methods of dream interpretation. Some people such as Freud us secular forms of psychology to interpret dreams through psych analysis. I do not agree with the psychological view of dream interpretation entirely, psychology should be coupled with theology and an investigation of culture as well as considering the background and emotional state of the dreamer.
